@item NC_NOERR
No error.

@item NC_NOMEM
Out of memory.

@item NC_EHDFERR
HDF5 error. (NetCDF-4 files only.)

@item NC_EDIMMETA
Error in netCDF-4 dimension metadata. (NetCDF-4 files only.)

@item NC_ENOCOMPOIND
(NetCDF-4 files only.)

